    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Grid convergence (GCI 3.2%) and output comparison (NIH within 18%) demonstrate sufficient predictive capability for the COU decision. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed across all 5 operating points. Model credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
